    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is mechanically superlative, with a documented dual-VANOS overhaul and preventative rear subframe reinforcement using Turner Motorsport plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a perfectly functioning M-Variable differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with no bushing deflection or damper leakage. Finished in Alpine White over Nappa leather, the interior shows zero bolster wear and no pixel degradation in the electronics. A turn-key, high-compression masterpiece for the technical purist.",
