      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled facility and driven only on the clearest of days. The exterior paint possesses a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or even the slightest superficial scratch. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash whatsoever. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary that still retains its new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, with zero creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. Every technological feature\u2014from the crystal-clear infotainment display to the ambient lighting\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new; the engine note is smooth and purposeful, and the transmission shifts are seamless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists, ensuring that no maintenance item has ever been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or an exacting driver to acquire a truly flawless, investment-grade vehicle.",
